<i>This way, please.</i>

527
00:37:40,405 --> 00:37:42,525
Mr. Ling, how should we deal
with Miss Xia?

528
00:37:42,605 --> 00:37:45,845
Have security look the other way.

529
00:37:46,485 --> 00:37:48,205
I'm really not a business spy.

530
00:37:48,285 --> 00:37:49,725
I just need to talk to Mr. Ling.

531
00:37:49,805 --> 00:37:52,245
We'll need to investigate
before we can be sure.

532
00:37:52,925 --> 00:37:53,805
Please cooperate.

533
00:37:54,085 --> 00:37:55,365
-I will.
-Please leave.

534
00:37:55,445 --> 00:37:57,565
Please don't call the police.

535
00:37:58,005 --> 00:37:58,845
Please leave now.

536
00:39:40,565 --> 00:39:42,325
Subtitle translation by Luke Deming

537
00:39:42,405 --> 00:39:44,965
Mr. Ling, marriage is something serious.

538
00:39:45,325 --> 00:39:47,245
Please don't joke around about my health.

539
00:39:48,245 --> 00:39:51,645
Ms. Xia, we're just taking
what we need from this marriage.

540
00:39:52,085 --> 00:39:54,645
Ling Yizhou, his best friend Chu Yan,

541
00:39:54,725 --> 00:39:57,125
and his assistant Wen Li
definitely have something going on.

542
00:39:57,205 --> 00:39:58,965
If that's not a love triangle, what is?

543
00:39:59,245 --> 00:40:04,725
So, he wants to marry me
to use me as his smokescreen.

544
00:40:05,005 --> 00:40:06,125
The reason isn't important.
